    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>The Hallway Track is a weekly curated link roundup published at hallway.aris.pub. We take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data.</p>
    <p>This policy complies with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and applies to all visitors and subscribers.</p>

    <h2>2. Data Controller</h2>
    <p>The data controller for The Hallway Track is:</p>
    <p><strong>Leo Torres</strong><br>
    Emilienstrasse 19<br>
