    Email: <a href="mailto:leo@leotrs.com">leo@leotrs.com</a></p>

    <h2>3. What Data We Collect</h2>
    <p>If you subscribe to the newsletter, we collect your <strong>email address</strong>. That is the only personal data we collect.</p>
    <p>We use <a href="https://umami.is">Umami</a> for privacy-respecting analytics. Umami does not use cookies, does not track individual users, and does not collect personal data. It records aggregate pageviews, referrers, and device information only.</p>

    <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
    <p>We process your email address based on your <strong>consent</strong> (Article 6(1)(a) GDPR) when you subscribe to the newsletter.</p>

    <h2>5. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <p>We use your email address to send you the weekly newsletter. Nothing else.</p>

    <h2>6. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do NOT sell or rent your personal data. Your email address is shared only with our email service provider to deliver the newsletter.</p>

    <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Your email address is retained while your subscription is active and deleted upon unsubscribe.</p>

    <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Access</strong> your personal data</li>
        <li><strong>Rectify</strong> inaccurate data</li>
        <li><strong>Erase</strong> your personal data</li>
        <li><strong>Restrict</strong> processing</li>
        <li><strong>Data portability</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Object</strong> to processing</li>
        <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> at any time</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:leo@leotrs.com">leo@leotrs.com</a>.</p>
    <p>You can unsubscribe from the newsletter at any time using the link in each email.</p>

    <h2>9. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data, including encrypted connections (HTTPS) and secure data storage.</p>

    <h2>10. International Transfers</h2>
    <p>The website is hosted within the European Union. If any subprocessors are based outside the EU, transfers are protected by the EU-US Data Privacy Framework and standard contractual clauses.</p>

    <h2>11. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>This website is not intended for users under 16 years of age. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

    <h2>12. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Significant changes will be noted on the website.</p>

    <h2>13. Complaints</h2>
    <p>If you have concerns about how we handle your data, you have the right to lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.</p>

